			<div class="postrow">
				
				
				<h2 class="title icon icon0">
					The Expanse
				</h2>
				

						
							
							
							
						
						
				<div class="content ">
					<div id="post_message_1833200">
						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							I don't know if this has been discussed here yet but I just finished the second book of this series and wow, is it good. It's been a while since I've picked up a book that I found this hard to put down. If you don't know, the story takes place in an intra-solar system society where travel is between planets and asteroids. No FTL and inertial physics play a big role. The whole time I was reading this I kept thinking how well it would translate to a TV series so I started looking around and low and behold, Scyfy picked it up and made a series out of it. Not only did they order it, it is finished and will be coming out sometime this year. I looked at the trailer and it looks like they did a really good job with it, like Battlestar Galactica quality on the show.<br />
<br />

<iframe class="restrain" title="YouTube video player" width="640" height="390" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/8X5gXIQmY-E?wmode=opaque" frameborder="0"  allowfullscreen webkitallowfullscreen  mozallowfullscreen ></iframe>

						</blockquote>
					</div>

					
				</div>
			</div>
			
