						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							Just finished the second episode, its great so far.  Nice and dark and realistic, really interesting to see if our technology eventually comes close to that in the distant future.  Also childhood's end is good so far too.  Pretty great the scifi channel is getting back in order with all these great shows.<br />
<br />
My only gripe with expanse is that with all that future tech you would think they would make really effective water recycling systems, especially since they are in mostly closed environments.  Also I guess it could have more AI, but I guess it would lose the human feel they have going on with it.<br />
<br />
